>> dropping duplicates
    .drop_duplicates()
        .removes duplicate rows from a dataframe based on all columns or specific ones 
            .retains the first occurrence of each row and removes any duplicates that follow 
        .give (keep='last') argument to retain the last occurrence 
        .give (keep=False) argument to remove all rows that are duplicates 
    
    .use inplace=True to modify the dataframe in place without creating a new one 


